    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://losangeles.craigslist.org/sgv/sec/6042843335.html"></div>
        </div>
Flintridge Sacred Heart Academy, a Catholic, Dominican, independent, college-preparatory, day and boarding school, is currently looking for a part-time Driver to assist in transporting students Monday through Thursday, from 2:00pm-7:00pm, and Friday, from 1:00pm-7pm, in a 9-passenger school van.  This is a temporary position with the possibility of transitioning to a permanent, part-time position.  The rate of pay is $13/hr.  The Driver may be called upon to assist with campus traffic control, various school events, inspections of safety and van equipment, and provide facilities support as needed.     <br>
<br>
The qualified candidate must: <br>
•	be over 25 years of age  <br>
•	have a valid California driver's license and auto insurance  <br>
•	submit to and pass a background and MVR check  <br>
•	successfully pass a van operational safety test conducted by our Traffic Safety Team <br>
<br>
In addition, the qualified candidate will be courteous, have effective problem solving skills, excellent communication and interpersonal skills, and always be respectful of students, parents, faculty, and staff according to the Mission of Flintridge Sacred Heart Academy.   <br>
<br>
If you are interested in this position, please send your cover letter and resume to humanresources@fsha.org.<br>
    </section>

